      • event

        public B event()
        Complete configuration of a DelinquencyProcessEvent. Not much happens here; the DelinquencyPlanReason triggers the event creation when the reason itself is created. Mainly event() provides glue for Builder use.
        Returns:
        the DelinquencyPlanReasonBuilder which owns this event.
